<br>
You have to be incredibly crafty or fast in order to kill a mage that has a pet up.  Plus their post 50 spells can put in some serious hurting. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umadelinetz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Madeline TZ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/17/00 2:23:23 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.geocities.com/kaydenjadir/personalpic.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Mages?</span><hr size=1> Bah what happened to my personal pic?  It's fine everywhere else... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ufreonsmurf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>FreonSmurf</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC= http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_star.gif  BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/17/00 3:55:40 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://hoels76.tripod.com/wee.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Mages?</span><hr size=1> All I can say is stick on the owner of the pet.<br>
